threats.title: Data Breaches
threats.description: Users that dont have the correct the clearance can easily gain access from using other people login or their computers
threats.mitigation: Provide level access system that allow the admin/Manager to only a selected individual to have certain permission levels to gain access to relevant information

threats.title: Data leak
threats.description: Previously had the database as the central hub for the company however that posses a greater risk for data breaches
threats.mitigation: To prevent this we have relocated the database from the center and only allowed the cloud management to have access which prevents data leaks and breaches
